thread.title: Visitor from Dubai
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Visitor from Dubai

author: Visitor from Dubai
title: Visitor from Dubai
text: The car was ready with smile, and it was received with a thank you & smile. My booking was till 4:30, I was offered to drive the car back at any time after 4:30 and just drop the key in the key box. Everything wall well organized. I will use and recommend Omega Rental to my friends.
